node.text:
For #WorldRefugeeDay, I got the chance to swap stories of home with an incredible person. @mi.nnie_san lives in Denver, but was born in a refugee camp.⁣
⁣
It was a moving experience for me and a reminder that we all have a part to play making sure @refugees feel welcome.⁣
⁣
#WithRefugees #RefugeeDay

node.text:
#repost @kalinginternational
・・・
@sundanceorg is celebrating 40 years of supporting independent artists! ✨ To celebrate, we’re sharing some of our favorite photos from past years. 

At @kalinginternational, we strongly believe in the importance of storytelling from diverse voices, and that’s why we love @sundanceorg so much! If you are able, please consider donating now to help the next generation of independent storytellers via the link in our bio. #Sundance40th
